{"tid":609380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉於商場偷拍裙底拍著警嫂 休班警被控今提堂","createTime":"2018-03-29T04:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T04:14:24.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7330649d913048da1c330817c8768ae7ff10a1d8","tid":609380,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180329/large/1522292448_581b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180329%2Flarge%2F1522292448_581b.jpg&h=42676eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n45歲休班警涉在油塘商場扶手電梯偷拍警嫂裙底，案件今在觀塘法院提訊。他被控作出有違公德行為罪，暫時毋須答辯，辯方需時索閱審訊用文件及向休班警提供法律意見，裁判官將案押後至5月10日再訊，准以現金5,000元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指45歲被告莊志強於去年11月27日，於油塘大本型商場的地下至二樓、二樓至三樓的扶手電梯作出性質猥褻、令人憎惡的有違公德行為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oz8xrsRf3FJYYmBJS/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oz8xrsRf3FJYYmBJS%2Fgiphy.gif&h=656b7689&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}